  "riddle": "1. Unearth the storyteller who chronicled the resilience of the Japanese American community. In his works, how many unique titles does he offer to the world?\n\n2. From your discovery, transform it into its binary essence. How many 1-bits dance in the shadows of that number?\n\n3. Seek the grand institution of creativity nestled in a city known for its neon glow. What year was this temple of art brought to life?\n\n4. Gaze upon the heights where this cultural haven resides — what is its elevation above sea level?\n\n5. Journey into the world of reviews and accolades. What star rating does this renowned institution earn from its visitors?\n\n6. Draw together the two nuggets you have from clues 4 and 5. What emerges when you combine these values, forging a new number?\n\n7. Nearby, a tapestry of culture unfolds. Count how many other museums you can find in close proximity to your last stop.\n\n8. Turn your attention to a narrative adaptation that has captured hearts across the globe. When did this tale first grace the screens?\n\n9. Now, calculate the final key: take the absolute difference between the value from clue 2 and clue 4, and then apply the modulus of 10 to it. What single digit do you uncover?",
